Investment portfolio management | otris software AG






















































 










































For corporate groups
For municipalities
For private equities
Demo
 












Trust your investment portfolio management to an impartial process.





 


Investment portfolio management software makes it easier to successfully manage your investment structures




Manage your investment portfolios with otris corporate: You will gain a group-wide overview of all the information in your corporate group. Interconnections within the group structures are documented. Relationships within the individual companies are illustrated. Relationship histories become traceable and comprehensible, serving as a basis for the development of your investment concepts. 


 


From the perspective of a group of companies, investment portfolios should achieve a financial return and contribute to the fulfilment of corporate goals. Investment portfolio management should implement the efficient organisation of all tasks that need to be addressed from the perspective of a group of companies in terms of investment portfolios, locations, investors and elected representatives. However, companies often work with isolated partial results, as assignments from the investment portfolio environment are performed by different specialist departments and not seen as an integral corporate task. The use of special software solutions has proven successful in obtaining fast and easy access to all the investment structures and corporate data.





In otris corporate, our software for investment portfolio management, all the important master data and key figures of the individual companies, as well as their investment portfolios, investors, representatives and committees, are centrally managed and clearly interlinked. Together with local data administration, the web-based software architecture of the central solution ensures that your data is consistent and up-to-date. When saving the data, all data and documents are
archived based on the closing date. This means that changes and the statuses of different versions are traceable at any time. The entire application can be reset at the touch of a button to any point in time, so that you always have access to the actual state of the time selected. Moreover, otris corporate can be quickly and easily adapted to meet your specific requirements.


 





„otris corporate ensures that we keep track of our current and former participation structure.“







                    Michael Schmolinske 
                


                    Legal Advisor Corporate Management, Eckert & Ziegler Strahlen- und Medizintechnik AG
                



 


otris corporate at a glance






Corporation-wide central database with corporate folders (such as master data, investment portfolios, investors or key figures)
Documentation of all documents from corporate, commercial and tax law
Complete archiving
Audit-proof data storage
Workflow-based deadline monitoring with escalation management
Occupancy coordination for committee and representative support
Standardised and customisable reports







Interactive charts
Comprehensive research functions
Full-text indexing
High-security authorisation and encryption concept
Flexible and economic licensing model
Interfaces to ERP, CRM or other systems
Individual modifications, tailored to meet our customers’ needs



 














Full transparency
