More transparency with investment portfolio management




otris corporate enables you to manage master data, key figures and documents for all the investment structures in a clear and well-structured manner.






One central portal for all your information
otris corporate affords you the maximum level of transparency. Business-critical documents and data are unified in one information platform so that all processes and deadlines can be centrally controlled. Companies, investment portfolios, investors, representatives and committees are organised in the form of digital folders that serve as a repository for the relevant master data and key figures. All documents and contracts are intelligently interlinked with each other and archived in a audit-proof manner.





All important documents in one central application
Documents are recorded locally from within the corporate environment and classified by types. All the investment portfolio documentation is linked with companies, transactions and mandates, whether it concerns contracts, protocols, entries or certificates.





Audit-proof archiving of all documents
In order to gain access to all the important data, three aspects are particularly important in the management of critical business documents: Audit-proof long-term storage, convenient search and filter functions as well as classification of documents. With the KPMG-certified archiving component, you benefit from the most modern archiving functions in accordance with legal requirements and guidelines.





Dates and Deadlines always in view
Active deadline management helps to avoid unnecessary risks. Expiring contracts, appointments to committees or upcoming audits and meetings are monitored and the group of persons responsible is reminded in advance by e-mail. A date and deadline calendar provides the necessary overview.






Committees. Centrally depicted and archived.




The group-wide occupancy of all committees is centrally depicted in the investment portfolio management software and each mandate is historically archived. You can simulate past constellations at the click of a button. You gain a transparent overview of all the functionaries and decision-makers in your companies and investment portfolios. In addition, you can display which committees are appointed by the individual companies, including the number, member name and host company. You can see upcoming replacements and keep an eye on all your current appointments. Related documents provide information about decisions, rulings and committee meeting minutes. Links to individual elected representatives mean you can clearly see which people are active in different positions within the group of companies. Interactive charts help to visualise current occupancies and make navigation easy.






Representatives. Consistently managed and supported.




A mandate is a time-limited function for a person on a company’s committee. All of a person’s mandates within a Group are jointly managed and the related appointments are coordinated across all representatives. All relationships of this kind are interlinked so that you can view the data from different perspectives. Each person’s occupancy situation can be visually depicted using diagrams. The individual committees’ meeting dates are recorded in a calendar so that scheduling conflicts can be detected early on. On request, the people involved can be reminded of their participation by e-mail. In addition, you will find a wide range of documents in the committees’ digital folders such as the invitation with the agenda of the next meeting as well as rulings and minutes from previous meetings that have already been archived.






  








Modern investment portfolio management for more transparency in the corporate group. otris corporate provides you with fast and easy access to all your investment structures and corporate data. It forms the basis for your strategic investment management.


 


Reliable and transparent controlling within investment portfolio management




The investment control feature integrated in otris corporate will support you in managing your investments. It monitors and informs you about what the individual companies within the group contribute to achieve the agreed objectives.






Integrative solution with local access rights
With otris corporate we offer a group-wide integrated software solution with local access rights. This creates a consistent information platform, which is updated immediately after data is input. Important data from subsidiaries, branches and investment portfolios can be seamlessly reported directly to the central corporate control, which can use the data immediately. All parties are thereby provided with the relevant information: Those responsible in the individual investment portfolios can view the data that is associated with their unit.
All the information within the investment network is available to corporate control for evaluation purposes, etc. A central, integrative software solution is especially relevant for monitoring individual investments as it channels all the data streams of the individual investment portfolios and visualises them using a company cockpit. While individual unit solutions, which are not compatible with each other, are able to represent the targets of the respective investment portfolios and companies in an isolated manner, they do not provide an overview from the perspective of the entire company.





Clear evaluations, charts and reports
In otris corporate, your ownership structure and investment portfolios are visually represented in organisational charts. From the organisational chart, you can call up individual companies at the click of a button for an immediate view of all the information in each unit, including: master data, key figures, investment portfolios, investors, elected representatives, documents and contracts.
Any data from investment portfolio management or other sources can be accessed via the integrated business intelligence solution as flexible reports in standard output formats and types of charts. Standardised key figures can be supplemented by additional indicators. Individual evaluations are carried out according to the relevant criteria and all reports are sent automatically and regularly to freely definable e-mail distribution lists.


 


Investment portfolio management offers efficient tools for investment management




otris corporate makes it easier for you to manage your investment portfolios by means of risk observation and investment portfolio simulations as well as the evaluation and analysis of key figures.






Uniform processes ensure high-quality data
Thanks to consistent process orientation, our software solution for investment portfolio management can support your investment management as an integrative solution. All the relevant data from your investment portfolios, branches and subsidiaries is recorded and processed via customisable workflows. For both local companies and corporate control, it’s important for all parties to have quick access to consistent data with quality information.





Complete company data simulation
When saving the data, all data and documents are archived based on the closing date, so that all changes and the statuses of different versions are traceable at any time. In addition, you can reset the entire application at the touch of a button to any point in time, so that you always have access to the reactivated, complete actual state of that point in time. This turns the assistance platform into your personal simulator for investment portfolio history.


 



